OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FAnas Sarwar is vowing to show Scots
OL,7,F"what change looks like" within the
OL,8,Ffirst 100 days of a Labour government,
OL,9,Fif he wins next week's Holyrood
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Labour leader is setting
OL,13,Fout his plans for the first 100,
OL,14,Fshould his party be successful in
OL,15,Fousting John Swinney's SNP from power
OL,16,Fon May 7.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@XO]
