OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FA week out from polling day, Mr Sarwar
OL,7,Fappealed to voters to give him five
OL,8,Fyears in power to "fix the mess" he
OL,9,Fsaid was caused by almost 20 years of
OL,10,Fthe SNP in power.
OL,12,FA Scottish Labour government would
OL,13,Fdeclare a waiting times emergency
OL,14,Fwithin its first 100 days ` with Mr
OL,15,FSarwar adding plans would also be
OL,16,Fdrawn up to ensure patients are
OL,17,Ftreated wherever there is capacity.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
