OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FIf the conflict in the Gulf continues,
OL,7,Fhe is also promising a #100 million of
OL,8,Femergency support to help with the
OL,9,Fcost of living ` with this including
OL,10,Fproposals to bring down the price of
OL,11,Fpetrol and diesel at the pump and
OL,12,Fsupport for businesses.
OL,14,FIn addition, Scottish Labour would
OL,15,Ftransfer the first #70 million into a
OL,16,Fnew fund for councils to repair
OL,17,Fpotholes on the roads, ban mobile
OL,18,Fphones in Scotland's classrooms and
OL,19,Fend the SNP's "ideological" ban on new
OL,20,Fnuclear power stations.
OL,26,@{D@OOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
