OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FLabour also says it would create a new
OL,7,Fending homelessness unit in the first
OL,8,F100 days, to start work to end rough-
OL,9,Fsleeping, create a Scottish Treasury
OL,10,Fin a bid to boost government
OL,11,Fefficiency and cut waste, and work
OL,12,Fwith CalMac and others to prevent a
OL,13,F"summer ferry crisis" from hitting
OL,14,FScotland's islands.
OL,16,FSpeaking seven days out from polling
OL,17,Fday, Mr Sarwar said: "We have all seen
OL,18,Fthe mess John Swinney and the SNP have
OL,19,Fmade over those 20 years.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@UO]yD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,F"Our NHS is struggling, family budgets
OL,7,Fare under pressure, our roads are
OL,8,Fcrumbling, and too many people feel
OL,9,Four country is stuck.
OL,11,F"The SNP has had 20 years and Scotland
OL,12,Fhas paid the price."
OL,14,FHowever, Mr Sarwar added: "My message
OL,15,Fto voters is simple: you've given the
OL,16,FSNP 20 years, give me five.
OL,18,F"Give me five years to fix the mess,
OL,19,Fget the basics right and build a
OL,20,Fbetter future for Scotland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@TO]vD@[OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
