OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,F"And, in our first 100 days, we will
OL,7,Fshow exactly what change looks like.
OL,9,F"That means emergency action to cut
OL,10,Fwaiting times and save our NHS;
OL,11,Fpractical help with the cost of
OL,12,Fliving; action to fix the roads;
OL,13,Fsupport to tackle homelessness; steps
OL,14,Fto get our economy moving; and a
OL,15,Fgovernment that respects taxpayers'
OL,16,Fmoney instead of wasting it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
