SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,F"And, if this international
OL,7,Finstability continues, we will not sit
OL,8,Fback and let Scottish families and
OL,9,Fbusinesses pay the price. We will act
OL,10,Fwith #100 million of emergency support
OL,11,Fin our first 100 days."
OL,13,FSNP leader Mr Swinney has already said
OL,14,Fhe will be "hitting the ground
OL,15,Frunning" if he wins the election.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]vD@LOUwD@HO]
