OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FIn proposals outlined on Monday, he
OL,7,Fset out how action would be taken
OL,8,Ftowards an independence referendum
OL,9,Fwithin 100 days ` along with plans to
OL,10,Fintroduce a price cap for some
OL,11,Fessential food items.
OL,13,FThe SNP also proposes to open five new
OL,14,Fwalk-in GP clinics within 100 days, as
OL,15,Fwell as rolling out a #2 cap on bus
OL,16,Ffares to some parts of Scotland, while
OL,17,Fup to 2,000 first-time home buyers
OL,18,Fcould get up to #10,000 of help to get
OL,19,Fon the property ladder with the
OL,20,Fplanned first homes fund.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
