CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FGeorge Adam, SNP candidate for
OL,7,FPaisley, said: "We don't need this
OL,8,Fflimsy document to know what a Labour
OL,9,Fgovernment would be like ` we can see
OL,10,Fit every day that Keir Starmer is in
OL,11,Foffice.
OL,13,F"The reality is that Labour are asking
OL,14,Fpeople to vote for an opposition to
OL,15,Fstop things from happening ` the SNP
OL,16,Fare asking for people to vote for a
OL,17,Fgovernment that will get things done.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
