OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777521849
OL,3,CLabour will show Scots 'what change
OL,4,Clooks like', vows Anas Sarwar
OL,6,F"The SNP want to bring down people's
OL,7,Fbills ` and the other parties want to
OL,8,Fstop us. We will bring down the cost
OL,9,Fof people's commute with a #2 bus fare
OL,10,Fcap, introduce price caps on essential
OL,11,Ffoods and give families more support
OL,12,Fwith childcare.
OL,14,F"The best way to ensure we can deliver
OL,15,Fis by electing a majority SNP
OL,16,Fgovernment ` and next week people can
OL,17,Fvote for an SNP government under the
OL,18,Ftrusted, reliable leadership of John
OL,19,FSwinney."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@IO]
